reference_reason: No relevant information found in reference_context.
model_reason: The DU failed to start because the CU could not be bound to the 'lo' interface. Since the CU and DU are likely running on different machines as implied by their IP addresses (127.0.0.5 and 127.0.0.3 for CU and DU loopback addresses respectively are not possible if it's the same machine), the 'local_s_if_name' on the CU should be set to an actual network interface such as 'eth0' to enable communication between the CU and DU.
